<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Can</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">llarca Elif</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">te ne buldu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">unu anlamak g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Hele de etraf</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">bir</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ok kad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nla </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">evrili, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">bir oyuncuyken. Zor dostum zor! Ama Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">le belki de bamba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ka bir y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ne do</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ru ilerliyor. Gazetelerde isimsiz olarak </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kan sahte evliliklerinden </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">phelenen </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">İ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">smail Dede ikiliyi kontrol etmek istedi. A</span><span style="font-weight: 40