<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Can ve Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n ayn</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yata</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a girmeleri, Can</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n eve onlarca </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ek g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ndermesi ve finalde Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e olan duygular</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">dile getirmesi </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">c</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Afrodizyak etkili bitki </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">tiklerinde </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">iftimize olanlar da hayli ilgin</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ti. G</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lmedik de</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">il </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">imdi. Birbirimizi kand</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rmayal</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m. Ayr</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ca b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">inde s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k geri d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ler, oldu. Daha </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ok tekrar diyebiliriz buna. </span></p>
