<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bunun d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ışı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nda Can ve Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l at</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ış</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">malar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">daha da bir sevmeye ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m. Keyifli oluyor. Her ne kadar b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k oyuncu Can</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n ac</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">halleri bana garip gelse de e</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lenceli. Hele Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e reklam teklifi geldi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">indeki halleri daha do</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rusu kurdu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">u hayaller! Baya</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> baya</span><span style="font-weight: 4