<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bekle be k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m! Her </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ey g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zel olacak. A</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">as</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Murat ve Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l olurmu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">gibi geliyordu ama d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e ve g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e uzakla</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">şı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yorum bu fikirden. Elif ise t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">oyunlar pe</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">inde. O da ne istedi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ini bilmiyor. Triplerden trip be</span><span style="font-weight: 4