<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vee Eda'ya ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nderem gizemli ki</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">i belli oldu! Ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ak! </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&Uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">stelik de o bir kameraym</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ış</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Yani </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ok doksanlar bir taktik ama </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ok da ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Ben Ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ak'</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n neden bu kadar k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">oldu</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">unu anlamad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m. Sanki k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">olmak zorunda gibi. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&Ccedil;&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kameradan izlerken falan bir ara yumu</s